              <text x="136" y="228" fill="#4f46e5" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle">lo premia, lo admira,</text>
              <text x="136" y="244" fill="#4f46e5" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle">lo recompensa</text>
              <text x="136" y="266" fill="#64748b" font-size="10.5" font-style="italic" text-anchor="middle">"el humilde es honrado"</text>
