              <text x="424" y="228" fill="#b91c1c" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle">lo castiga, lo ridiculiza,</text>
              <text x="424" y="244" fill="#b91c1c" font-size="11" text-anchor="middle">lo desprestigia</text>
